<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="government-n">government <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɡʌvənmənt/    美 /'ɡʌvərnmənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>政府；内阁：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>set up a government
建立政府；组阁</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The Prime Minister has <strong>formed</strong> a new <strong>government</strong>.
首相已组建了新内阁。</p></div>

<p>注: government作主语时，如果作为整体看待，谓语动词用单数；如果强调政府成员，谓语动词用复数。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The new government has come into office. 
新政府已开始执政。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The government are discussing the proposal. 
政府正在讨论这项提案。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>政体；统治；管理：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>communist government
共产政体</p></div></div>